} }; const exportToExcel = () => { const csvContent = recentOrders.map(order => `${order.id},${order.customer},${order.amount},${order.status},${order.date},${order.deadline}` ).join('\n'); const blob = new Blob([csvContent], { type: 'text/csv' }); const url = window.URL.createObjectURL(blob); const a = document.createElement('a'); a.href = url; a.download = 'orders.csv'; a.click(); }; return (
